OL,4,CRemington: US gunmaker offers $33m to
OL,5,CSandy Hook shooting victims
OL,6, The company that made a rifle used in
OL,7, one of the worst school shootings in
OL,8, the US has offered $33m (#24m) to
OL,9, several victims' families.
OL,11,FThe proposed settlement for the 2012
OL,12,FSandy Hook massacre from Remington,
OL,13,FAmerica's oldest gun-maker, came as
OL,14,Fpart of a bankruptcy hearing for the
OL,15,Fcompany.
OL,17,FIt also comes in response to a lawsuit
OL,18,Fbrought by families of nine of the 26
OL,19,Fvictims.
OL,21,FEach family would receive some $3.66m.
